{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Make a paste of fenugreek seeds which have been soaking in water for a while. Rub some coconut oil into your scalp. Next take the fenugreek seed paste, and apply it to the hair. Allow the paste to remain on your hair for an hour, then wash it out. Continue this routine for a month for optimal results. This will strengthen your hair and help to prevent future hair loss.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-a-woman-in-the-bedroom.jpg\" class=\"img_left \" alt=\"portrait of a woman in the bedroom\" style=\"float: left; padding: 8px; padding-left: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you have to dye your hair, have it done by a professional. Request that they use foils, instead of a hair dye. The dye&#39;s chemicals should not touch your scalp since they can damage your scalp and follicles and lead to hair loss.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Many women who are losing a lot of hair are surprised to learn that it is&nbsp;caused by hormonal issues. Birth control can cause a hormonal imbalance, and lead to&nbsp;hair loss. Even therapy for hormone replacement can sometimes create a temporary hormonal imbalance. If you are <a href=\"advice-for-those-who-have-hair-loss-problems\"  >dealing with hair loss<\/a>, be sure to check your hormone levels.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/photo-of-different-high-protein-foods.jpg\" class=\"img_right \" alt=\"photo of different high protein foods\" style=\"float: right; padding: 8px; padding-right: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before going through chemotherapy, shave or cut your hair. This will help you to feel in control and powerful, rather than powerless when it comes to your hair.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Include lots of protein in your diet to help curb hair loss. Adapt your diet so that you are not suffering from a protein deficiency, which could result in hair loss. Keep exposure to toxins and pollutants to a minimum to maintain a full, beautiful head of hair. Substances that are unhealthy inside your body drive down your general health, and when your body is having a difficult time staying healthy, your chances of having thinning hair or hair loss are higher. Foods that are high in protein may help you regrow lost hair.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is no longer any reason to feel sad as you watch your hair disappear down the drain. Knowing&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/hairgrowthreport.org\/hair-growth-information\/how-to-naturally-improve-hair-growth\"  >how to grow your hair back<\/a>, is priceless. Ensure you utilize the above advice, and you can get started immediately. Hopefully, you&#39;ll notice a vast difference with the amount of hair on your head very soon. We hope you found these tips useful.<\/p>\r\n"}